videos.headline: Texas A&M takes opening kick back for TD
videos.description: Jashaun Corbin gets Texas A&M on the board early as he takes back the opening kickoff 100 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Williams powers in for a 1-yard TD
videos.description: Trayveon Williams rushes in for his fifth touchdown of the year to extend Texas A&M's lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Kelley recovers high snap to rush in for a 1-yard TD
videos.description: Arkansas quarterback Cole Kelley recovers from a high snap to rush in for a 1-yard touchdown

videos.headline: Williams walks in for a  4-yard TD
videos.description: Trayveon Williams rushes in for a 4-yard touchdown to extend Texas A&M's lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Arkansas' Storey finds WR for a 29-yard TD
videos.description: Arkansas won't go away as Ty Storey throws to Michael Woods for a 29-yard touchdown.
